plot: Jim Jefferies is a globally renowned Australian stand-up, hailed by critics and loved by legions of fans. In FULLY FUNCTIONAL, Jim tells us true life stories filled with good intentions wrapped up in deviant behaviour. In HD.
title: Jim Jefferies: Fully Functional
